short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copy HTML, CSS, and JavaScript from webpages

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Website Extractor allows users to seamlessly extract HTML, CSS, and JavaScript from any webpage. This powerful and intuitive tool is perfect for developers, designers, and learners who want to explore how a website is built.

Key Features:

Extract HTML, CSS, and JavaScript from specific elements or the entire webpage.
Built-in options to include or exclude specific code types.
Easy-to-use interface with real-time feedback.
Save extracted code directly or copy it to the clipboard.

Why Use Website Extractor?

Learn coding techniques by analyzing real-world websites.
Reuse styles and scripts for personal projects.
